lead_paragraph: Cal O'Reilly and Johan Larsson each scored twice and the Buffalo Sabres extended their home dominance over the Toronto Maple Leafs with a 4-1 victory Thursday night.

headline.print_headline: Cal O'Reilly, Larsson Lead Sabres Over Maple Leafs 4-1
